high_descs: Turn left for four steps, turn left again and take seven steps and turn left to face the tub.
Pick up the candle closest to you.
Turn right for one step, turn right again and take two steps and stop.
Open the left bottom cabinet door, under the sink on the right side, put the candle in the cabinet and shut the door.
Turn around and walk two spaces and stop.
Pick up the candle on the right.
Turn around and walk two spaces and stop.
Open the left bottom cabinet door, under the sink on the right side, put the candle in the cabinet to the right of the first candle, and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles in the bottom left cabinet, under the right sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the side of the bathtub.
Pick up the candle closest to the corner of the lip of the tub.
Turn around and walk to the middle of the sinks.
Put the candle in the left cabinet under the right sink.
Turn around and walk back to the tub.
Pick up the candle on the side of the tub.
Turn around and face the sinks again.
Place the candle in the left cabinet under the right sink, to the right of the other candle.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left, step forward, then turn  left and go to the corner of the bath tub.
Pick up the candle closer to the left edge of the tub.
Turn right, step forward, then right and step forward to the bathroom cabinets.
Open the left side door on the bottom right cabinet, place the candle inside and close the door.
Turn around and return to the edge of bath tub.
Pick up the candle on the bath tub.
Turn around and return the bathroom cabinets.
Open the same cabinet door as before, place the candle inside, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place two candles in the bathroom cabinet.
